text: Steinle is a German-language surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Eduard Von Steinle (1810–1886), an Austrian painter * Roland J. Steinle (1896–1966), an American judge * Ulla Steinle, a West German canoeist * Moritz Steinle (born 1983), a German footballer * Kathryn Steinle (19822015), an American woman fatally shot by an illegal alien in 2015 == See also == * Steinle Turret Machine Company, a historic building in Madison, Wisconsin Category:German-language surnames
